{"word":"G352 - ἀνακύπτω - anakýptō - an-ak-oop'-to - Lift up","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀνακύπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anakýptō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-ak-oop'-to</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Lift up</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நிமிர், நிமிர்ந்துப்பார்"},{"paragraph":"to raise or lift oneself up"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G303 - ἀνά - aná - an-ah'/303\">G303</a> (in the sense of <i>reversal</i>) and <a href=\"#/G2955 - κύπτω - kýptō - koop'-to/2955\">G2955</a>; to <i>unbend</i>, that is, <i>rise</i>; figuratively <i>be elated:</i> - lift up, look up.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}